sentences.sContent: Officials with the Mississippi Department of Wildlife, Fisheries and Parks (MDWFP) said it could be the largest alligator gar caught.
sentences.sContent_eng: Officials with the Mississippi Department of Wildlife, Fisheries and Parks (MDWFP) said it could be the largest alligator gar caught.
sentences.sCn: 野生动物、鱼类和公园(MDWFP)的密西西比河部门的官员说它是被逮住的最大的鳄雀鳝。

sentences.sContent: Looking for all the world like the cross between an alligator, a fish and dinosaur, the alligator gar is the largest freshwater fish in America.
sentences.sContent_eng: Looking for all the world like the cross between an alligator, a fish and dinosaur, the alligator gar is the largest freshwater fish in America.
sentences.sCn: 寻遍全世界鳄鱼、鱼和恐龙的杂交后代，鳄雀鳝是美国一种最大的淡水鱼。
